snippet.title: Slay the Princess – Halloween '22 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A spooky season demands a spooky trailer.

Keep your eyes peeled for some quick teasers of what's to come in the full release, and check out the Slay the Princess trailer as part of Steam Next Fest from October 3rd to October 10th.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989270/Slay_the_Princess/
